{"id": "1451727637595553974", "channel_id": "1451724086945513502", "type": 0, "author_id": "516998769888329749", "author_name": "zzzorz", "author_bot": false, "content": "軟化のところだけよくわからないんですけど、これはどのような？", "timestamp": "2025-12-20T00:07:20.598000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1451724086945513502", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "代入するだけダメージ計算式", "forum_channel_id": "1391703584755941467"}
{"id": "1451741009141694484", "channel_id": "1451724086945513502", "type": 0, "author_id": "516998769888329749", "author_name": "zzzorz", "author_bot": false, "content": "×(0.2+0.1f)かなと思っていたのですがー", "timestamp": "2025-12-20T01:00:28.623000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "👍", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1451724086945513502", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "代入するだけダメージ計算式", "forum_channel_id": "1391703584755941467"}
{"id": "1451741132819005580", "channel_id": "1451724086945513502", "type": 0, "author_id": "735553627539898400", "author_name": "kara4691", "author_bot": false, "content": "軟化は受けるダメージ20%、軟化1につき10%増加という効果なので\n軟化1　20+10%、\n軟化2　20+20%、\n軟化3　20+30%\n\nなので\n1+0.2+0.1f\nで求められます\n\nしかしこの式のままにすると軟化0の時に火力が1.2倍になってしまいます\n↓\n1+0.2+0=1.2\n\nなので間に（f÷f）をかませて0の時は0.2が消滅するようにしました<:yurui:1390952967414354020> \n\n軟化層数上限は書き忘れです！編集しておきました！", "timestamp": "2025-12-20T01:00:58.110000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1451724086945513502", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "代入するだけダメージ計算式", "forum_channel_id": "1391703584755941467"}
{"id": "1451741543286181888", "channel_id": "1451724086945513502", "type": 0, "author_id": "516998769888329749", "author_name": "zzzorz", "author_bot": false, "content": "なーるほど", "timestamp": "2025-12-20T01:02:35.973000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1451724086945513502", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "代入するだけダメージ計算式", "forum_channel_id": "1391703584755941467"}
